subject: Soccer
Extradition
Bribery and Kickbacks
organizations: Confederation of North, Central American and Caribbean Association Football (CONCACAF)
lead_paragraph: Webb, a former president of Concacaf and a vice president of FIFA who was arrested in May, has agreed to extradition and is currently in the United States.
